VALUES ('BUTTON_AUTHZ_INCONSISTENCY', 'I can confirm both page and next button have the same Authorization scheme, Global_Base_Auth.', 1, 5, 'The justification directly addresses the access control concern by explaining how equivalent or stronger authorization is enforced at the relevant boundary. It gives enough context to show the finding is a credible false positive or acceptable-by-design case.');
